      • escape

        public static final byte[] escape(java.lang.String s)
        Escapes a string into the required Oracle flat file format. In one scan from left to right, a % is replaced with %25, a tab \t is replaced with %09, a newline \n is replaced with %0A, and a comma is replaced with %2c.
        Parameters:
        s - the string to be escaped
        Returns:
        a byte array representation of the escaped string.
